Application is currently deployed on Heroku: http://cold-leaf-1834.heroku.com/

Before production deployment to heroku server, compile current assets to public folder and commit changes:
RAILS_ENV=production bundle exec rake assets:precompile 

Action Mailer is set to use SendGrid external SMTP service. Following variables need to be provided:
heroku config:add SMTP_USER=sendgrid_username
heroku config:add SMTP_PASSWORD=sendgrid_password